National Seminar Held in Thailand 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 19 (KCNA) -- A national seminar on the Juche idea was held in Thailand on Feb. 11 on the occasion of the birthday of leader Kim Jong Il and the 30th anniversary of the proclamation of the programme for modeling the whole society on the Juche idea.
 Songchit Pullarp, chairman of the Organization for the Study of the Juche Idea of Thailand, in his report at the seminar said they were recalling with deep emotion the great exploit Kim Jong Il performed by formulating the revolutionary idea of President Kim Il Sung as an integral system of idea, theory and method of Juche on the occasion of the birthday of Kim Jong Il and the 30th anniversary of the proclamation of the programme for modeling the whole society on the Juche idea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Noting that Kim Jong Il created the original Songun politics based on the Juche idea, thus defending the dignity of the country and the sovereignty of the nation and leading the building of a great prosperous powerful nation to victory, he said he would actively disseminate the most just and advantageous Juche idea among the Thai people and apply it to practice. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Then followed speeches titled "On the Juche idea", "The reality of Korea in which the Juche idea is embodied", "The Songun politics and the Juche idea of Korea" and "The Juche idea and the social development".

Passage of Amendment to Law on Foreign Exchange in Japan Condemned 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 19 (KCNA) -- An enlarged extraordinary meeting of the Central Committee of the Czechoslovak Communist Party was held in Prague on February 11 as regards the passage of an "amendment to the law on foreign exchange" through the Japanese House of Representatives.
 Participants in the meeting charged that Japan is posing a great danger to peace and stability in the Korean peninsula, Asia and the world by recently worsening the DPRK-Japan relations to the extreme, whose typical example is the fact that the Japanese reactionary rulers passed the amendment through the House of Representatives on January 29. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Japanese reactionaries, they said, have been disqualified not only to have a bilateral contact with the DPRK but to participate in the six-way talks slated for the end of February owing to their reckless hostile policy toward the DPRK. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 At the meeting General Secretary of the Central Committee of the Czechoslovak Communist Party Miroslav Stepan made public a statement. 
 He stressed in the statement that Japan's amendment is a grave infringement upon the sovereignty of the DPRK to isolate it in the international arena by taking advantage of the U.S. hostile policy toward the DRPK, a frantic violation of the international law and a vicious challenge to the DPRK-Japan Pyongyang Declaration. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He said the Czech progressive public considers that the DPRK should unconditionally prevent Japan from having any bilateral contact with it and participating in the forthcoming six-way talks.

Kim Jong Il Praised 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 19 (KCNA) -- Elena Scherbakova, head of the MoiseyevState Academy Folk Dance Troupe of Russia on a visit to the DPRK, was interviewed by KCNA at Yanggakdo International Hotel on Feb. 18 before its departure from here.
Referring to her great honor of being received by leader Kim Jong Il, she said that he spared time to see the performance given by the troupe despite the pressure of his work to administer all affairs of the country. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 She went on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The troupe came to Korea with its program comprising peculiar and colorful numbers prepared with all sincerity to join the Korean people in significantly celebrating his birthday. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Kim Jong Il is known to Russia as a distinguished leader wisely leading the Workers' Party of Korea, the army and the people. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Kim Jong Il, chairman of the DPRK National Defence Commission, is a dear friend of the Russian people and a genius of arts. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He has always taken deep care of the troupe and bestowed great benevolence upon it each time it visited the DPRK. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 We will always keep this kindness in mind. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The troupe will as ever conduct more vigorous art activities to contribute to the development of the Russia-DPRK friendship carrying with it the warm feelings of friendship of the Russian people towards the Korean people.

Measures for Ending Discrimination against Part-time Workers Urged in S. Korea 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 19 (KCNA) -- The (south) Korean Confederation of Trade Unions issued a statement on Feb. 14 demanding the authorities take immediate measures for the withdrawal of the part-time work system.
 In that early morning Pak Il Su, worker of Hyundai Heavy Industries Co.,Ltd., committed self-immolation after leaving behind a testament calling for the abolition of part-time work, the statement said, adding: It can not but feel pity and pain when seeing the wretched plight of the part-time workers. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 His self-immolation is not a suicide but a "social murder" by company owners who are increasing the number of part-time workers in quest of their profits and forcing them to lead a sub-human life and do slave labour and by the "government" which has not taken any measure for them, merely talking about the protection of part-time job. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 For the "government" and company owners to leave the part-time job as it is is a grave criminal act as it is aimed to hurt the humanity of workers and worsen the social inequality and widen the gap between the rich and the poor. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The confederation will not overlook the incident but create an organization to take measures and fight till the day the part-time workers are able to lead a life as human beings.

Immediate Dissolution of GNP Urged 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 19 (KCNA) -- The South Korean Federation of UniversityStudent Councils on Feb. 12 reportedly issued a statement titled "Dissolve the Grand National Party Protecting Scandals and Taking Money by Truck".
 Recalling that the "motion on releasing" So Chong Won, former representative of the GNP, was railroaded through the "National Assembly" at its plenary session on Feb. 9 by unsigned secret vote and So, kingpin of corruption, was "greeted" by "assemblymen from the GNP" upon his release, it said: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The remarks of Choe Pyong Ryol, representative of the GNP, that his party would return the illicit fund by selling the party building were clearly exposed to be a deceptive ruse and the GNP confirmed once again its true nature as a party of taking money by truck and protecting scandals. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The first way of preventing corruption is to immediately dissolve the GNP. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
It should give full accounts of its irregularities and corruption and dissolve itself at once. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It called on all the people to join efforts to immediately dissolve the GNP and hold "the elections to the 17th National Assembly without it" for a clean policy, a new policy.

National Seminar in Nigeria 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 19 (KCNA) -- A national seminar on the subject "the Sunof the 21st century" was held in Abuja, Nigeria, on Feb. 10 on the occasion of the February holiday.
 The chairman of the Nigerian National Committee for the Study of the Juche Idea in his report said leader Kim Jong Il is a genius of ideology and theory and distinguished statesman and practician who has comprehensively developed and enriched the Juche idea founded by President Kim Il Sung, adding Kim Jong Il's extraordinary political ability is displayed these days with added clarity. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He went on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 In the days of grim tests when other countries would have collapsed tens of times Kim Jong Il pursued the Songun policy to firmly defend the sovereignty of the country and socialism. This policy is a great driving force that helped bring unimaginable brilliant successes in the cause of the country's reunification and in foreign policy. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The secretary general of the committee in his speech said in the DPRK led by Kim Jong Il all the people are leading a happy life, benefiting by free medical care and free education, with the Juche idea coming into bloom in realities. The Korean people single-heartedly united around him are carrying through their just demand despite persistent moves of the "only super power" to stifle the DPRK. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The chairman of the Nigerian Group for the Study of the Juche Philosophy in a speech expressed his resolution to deeply study and disseminate Kim Jong Il's Songun policy and the Juche idea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 A message of greetings to Kim Jong Il was adopted at the seminar.

Floral Basket to Kim Jong Il
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 19 (KCNA) - Lansana Conte, president of the Republic of Guinea, sent a floral basket to the DPRK embassy in Conakry on Feb. 13 to congratulate leader Kim Jong Il on his birthday. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The chief of Protocol of the Presidency placed the floral basket before the portraits of President Kim Il Sung and Kim Jong Il at the embassy. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 On the occasion the chief of Protocol said to most significantly celebrate the birthday of Kim Jong Il is a traditional jubilee not only of the Korean people but of the Guinean people. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 I had the greatest honor of presenting the floral basket to Kim Jong Il on his birthday upon the authorization of the president, he said, and sincerely wished Kim Jong Il good health and success in the work.

Reception given by Libyan Diplomatic Envoy
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 19 (KCNA) -- Secretary of the People's Bureau of the Great Socialist People's Libyan Arab Jamahiriya here Ahmed Amer Al Muakkaf hosted a reception at the Taedonggang Club for the Diplomatic Corps on Wednesday evening on the occasion of the birthday of leader Kim Jong Il and the 30th anniversary of the proclamation of the programme for modeling the whole society on the Juche Idea.
 Present there were Choe Thae Bok, secretary of the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea, Kim Su Hak, minister of Public Health, Ryom Sun Gil, chairman of the Central Committee of the General Federation of Trade Unions of Korea and officials concerned. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Staff members of the Libyan People's Bureau were present there. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The secretary in his speech said that he was glad to join the Korean people in celebrating the birthday of Kim Jong Il and the 30th anniversary of the proclamation of the programme for modeling the whole society on the Juche Idea and offered warm congratulations to Kim Jong Il on the occasion of the significant days. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Noting that the Korean people have achieved great successes under the wise leadership of Kim Jong Il, he expressed the firm belief that the Korean people would attain progress, prosperity and reunification and certainly build a great prosperous powerful nation under the banner of the Songun politics. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Choe Thae Bok said that Kim Jong Il's birth as the son of the guerrillas of Mt Paektu was a great fortune of the nation as it acclaimed one more peerlessly great man in the history spanning 5000 years and a great auspicious event which promised a bright future and eternal prosperity of the country. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He said that Kim Jong Il has performed the great immortal exploits with his unique political ability, while leading the overall work of the Party, the state and the army for 40 odd years. He wished the Libyan people success in their work, expressing the belief that the relations between the two countries would steadily grow strong thanks to the common efforts.

Holding Higher Banner of Juche Idea under Songun Leadership Called for
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 19 (KCNA) -- Rodong Sinmun today editorially calls for holding higher the banner of the Juche idea under the Songun leadership of the Workers' Party Korea on the occasion of the 30th anniversary of leader Kim Jong Il's proclamation of the programme for modeling the whole society on the Juche idea.
 Stressing that as the revolutionary idea of President Kim Il Sung was formulated as the guiding idea of the era of independence and the programme for modeling the whole society on the Juche idea was proclaimed, there took place an epochal turn in carrying out the cause of Juche and the army and the people of the DPRK could vigorously advance along the road of the uninterrupted revolution despite the rigorous test of history, the editorial continues: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Our Party, army and people are faced with the weighty historic task to implement the idea and cause of the President to the letter, true to the Songun revolutionary leadership of the Party, on the basis of the proud victory and successes achieved under the banner of modeling the whole society on the Juche idea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Ours is the era of Songun and the Songun idea serves as a militant banner for implementing the idea and cause of Kim Il Sung. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Songun revolutionary cause is a continuation of the process of modeling the whole society on the Juche idea started by our Party and represents its new higher stage. The Songun idea serves as a guiding principle for the Korean revolution based on the revolutionary idea of the President and a political philosophy of Kim Jong Il for the final accomplishment of the revolutionary cause of Juche. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Modeling the whole society on the Songun idea provides a guarantee for fully meeting the requirements for modeling all members of the society on the Juche idea and successfully implementing the idea and cause of the President. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Underscoring the need to firmly protect, preserve and glorify the ideological and theoretical exploits performed by the President, the editorial calls for doing so, holding high the slogan "Let us arm ourselves more firmly with the revolutionary ideas of the Great Leader Comrade Kim Il Sung!" as a strategic slogan of the Korean revolution. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The whole Party and army and all people should unite close around the headquarters of the revolution in the transparent spirit of devotedly defending the leader and exert primary efforts to increase the capability of the army, the core of the state power, pursuant to the line of economic construction in the Songun era, it concludes.

Programme of Modeling Whole Party and Society on Juche Idea
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 19 (KCNA) -- February 19 is the 30th anniversary of the proclamation of the programme of modeling the whole party and society on the Juche idea in the Democratic People's Republic of Korea.
 In his historic address before party propaganda officials from across the country 30 years ago, leader Kim Jong Il formulated the revolutionary ideas of President Kim Il Sung as an integral system of ideology, theories and methods of Juche and proclaimed it as the supreme programme of the Workers' Party of Korea to model itself and society on the Juche idea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Since the programme was declared, the Korean party and people have convincingly advanced under the banner of the Juche idea, a  new and unique idea reflecting the demand of a new era in the human history, turning the country into a powerful socialist nation of Juche. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 With the policy of modeling the whole party on the Juche idea successfully implemented, the WPK has strengthened to be a glorious party of Kim Il Sung monolithic in ideology and leadership and united closely on the basis of the leader's ideas, and to be a tested political guide of the Korean revolution. And it has fully displayed its might and dignity as a vanguard of the working class guiding the popular masses' cause of independence. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Under Kim Jong Il's songun-based outstanding revolutionary leadership, the modeling of the whole army on the Juche idea has reached a high stage and the army has grown to be the pivot of the revolution, driving force of the Juche cause and invincible army defending the cause of the leader and the party, equipped with powerful offensive and defensive means. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 As the political mode of Juche has developed to be perfect humanics, the people have been reared to be new-type human beings with a revolutionary faith, clear conscience and strong sense of morality and the unity of the whole society around the headquarters of the revolution has been achieved on the highest level. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Korean people are now working hard to build a great prosperous powerful nation under difficult conditions, always sharing the same destiny with their leader. The fact is enough to prove the great vitality of the programme.

National Seminar Held
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 19 (KCNA) -- A national seminar the Juche idea was held at the People's Palace of Culture today to mark the 30th anniversary of the proclamation of the programme for modeling the whole society on the Juche idea.
Present at the seminar were Choe Thae Bok and Jong Ha Chol, secretaries of the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea, and other officials. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Speeches were made by Candidate Academician, Professor and Doctor Thae Hyong Chol, president of the Academy of Social Science, Prof. O Kil Bang, first vice-president of Kim Il Sung University, Jang In Su, secretary of the Pyongyang City Committee of the WPK, Ryang Kyong Bok, director and editor-in-chief of the Workers' Party of Korea Publishing House, Prof. And Dr. Cha Kyong Il, president of the Kim Il Sung Political University, and Choe Chil Nam, editor-in-chief of Rodong Sinmun. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Speakers explained and proved the immortal great exploits leader Kim Jong Il performed by formulating the revolutionary ideas of President Kim Il Sung as the monolithic system of idea, theory and method of Juche through his tireless ideological and theoretical activities for 30 years, perfecting it as the guiding idea and revolutionary philosophy of our Party and leading the revolution and construction to a brilliant victory with his seasoned leadership. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The fundamental character and undisputed advantages of the programme for modeling the whole society on the Juche idea lie in that it is a new perfect programme of the revolutionary Party as it has the revolutionary outlook on the leader as its core and it is run through with the outlook and an original programme of the Party which embodied the Juche-oriented theory of ideology, they said. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 They referred to the immortal exploits Kim Jong Il has performed for the Party and the revolution, the country and the people by advancing the programme for modeling the whole society on the Juche idea and wisely leading the struggle to arm all members of the society with the revolutionary idea of Kim Il Sung. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Recalling that Kim Jong Il carried forward and developed the President's idea and line of attaching importance to arms, the idea of giving priority to military affairs as required by the changed times and enforced the Songun policy, the effective political mode of Korean-style, thus protecting the destiny of the country, the nation and socialism and laying an eternal foundation for the building of a great prosperous powerful socialist nation, they underscored the need to glorify 21st century as the century of accomplishing the cause of Songun and as Kim Jong Il's glorious century. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  The seminar was held in an atmosphere overflowing with a revolutionary enthusiasm to intensify the struggle to complete the process of ideologically preparing all members of the society under the Songun revolutionary leadership of Kim Jong Il, true to the idea and cause of the President.
